title: Wizard of the Dark Side of the Moon
description:
Several years ago, MTV reported the Wizard of Oz and Pink Floyds Dark Side of the Moon seem to play in sync with one another. I saved you the work and put them together on one file, so you can see for yourself.

This is simply Pink Floyds Dark Side of the Moon CD and The Wizard of Oz DVD together for you to enjoy. 

Notes to watch for.....
   Music changes with scene changes
   Lyrics of songs similar to scenes in movie
   Music intensity changes with scene intensity
